trial = pd.DataFrame()
for b in list(data["brand"].unique()):
    for v in list(data["vehicleType"].unique()):
        z = data[(data["brand"] == b) & (data["vehicleType"] == v)]["price"].mean()
        trial = trial.append(pd.DataFrame({'brand':b , 'vehicleType':v , 'avgPrice':z}, index=[0]))#Bv
trial = trial.reset_index()
del trial["index"]
trial["avgPrice"].fillna(0,inplace=True)
trial["avgPrice"].isnull().value_counts()
trial["avgPrice"] = trial["avgPrice"].astype(int)
